description: The libraries contained in this experiment come from the whole cell fraction of independent growths of cell line GM12878. They are stranded PE76 Illumina GAIIx RNA-Seq libraries from rRNA-depleted and DSN normalized Poly-A- RNA > 200 nucleotides in size.
